{"tid":1744584,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭是臥底手足黎，一早清楚教你點贏","createTime":"2019-11-21T22:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T10:35:18.000Z","uid":277944,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"89d5c8eeba75be7e7cdb6ef7d59eed5e060859bb","tid":1744584,"uid":277944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:26:57.000Z","msg":"佢早說明佢乜都冇，只有幾萬個差佬而已<br />\n又說明了自已，最怕暴最怕亂<br />\n<br />\n軍警是她唯一的利器<br />\n除此以外，到處都是怕暴怕亂的春袋軟肋<br />\n<br />\n不明白港示威者，尤其前線勇的武的行動力最強的<br />\n怎麼會有興趣對準人家唯一的尖刀，一起死撞埋去呢<br />\n<br />\n抗爭是為了打贏警察？訴求是打敗對家唯一尖刀？<br />\n你打倒了一萬個警察，<br />\n政府會做的，恐怕不是去答應你半個訴求<br />\n而是用你的錢，多請二萬個黑警<br />\n<br />\n請想清楚，抗爭的對手完全不是警察<br />\n抗爭的手段更不應是用肉身去擺陣對抗各種高級現代武器<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：大家千萬別犯法，愛惜都是香港人的警察，街頭見在街尾亦失讓路閃"},{"pid":"5768a2e640e2f13993fb7dc8a3c21e66289ec88a","tid":1744584,"uid":4658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:30:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾po，拉"},{"pid":"df6d7f3b2318d5e80714e8533a6dd906a99eccfc","tid":1744584,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5768a2e640e2f13993fb7dc8a3c21e66289ec88a","tid":1744584,"uid":4658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:30:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾po，拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:39:16.000Z","msg":"點解？"},{"pid":"f22a6079f04073fb9ae260b52ae431b34861ad98","tid":1744584,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df6d7f3b2318d5e80714e8533a6dd906a99eccfc","tid":1744584,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5768a2e640e2f13993fb7dc8a3c21e66289ec88a","tid":1744584,"uid":4658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:30:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾po，拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:39:16.000Z","msg":"點解？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:43:56.000Z","msg":"感覺上好似幫緊閪警洗白"},{"pid":"74a1a645125d26517aabb3d5c3ee1aa5a7cd0132","tid":1744584,"uid":129848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f22a6079f04073fb9ae260b52ae431b34861ad98",